{
  "stem": "5970.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had these primitive latrines, hundreds of rows of these wooden things and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very primitive, but they were still there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if you're used to it, you kept yourself clean as much as you could obviously.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were sent to work in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there were lots of beatings there and lots of hangings there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every morning, you used to see people hanging from ropes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the worst of all these places was the standing on a Pilplatz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In every camp, in every concentration camp, there was a big square where they used to count us every morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So now, we were wakened about 5 o'clock, sometimes 4 o'clock in the morning, by the Jewish supervisors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to stand there outside in rows for hours because the Germans only came about 8 o'clock or whenever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to stand there for hours outside waiting for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they used to count everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they used to send us to work in groups of 10 again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "At the beginning, when I was in Plaszow, they used to give us back breaking work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a quarry somewhere nearby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had to push trolleys full of stones, sometimes uphill, sometimes straight.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We never knew where these trolleys were going and what it was for.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we had to push them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was hard work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It wasn't for women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It wasn't for young people, for young girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It wasn't for children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But we have to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we did that for quite a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then things-- a lot of things happened all of a sudden, after a few weeks when we were in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
